only, no service-assembly restructure", or (b) move default construction to a 
sub-factory that `createTriggersServiceContext` delegates to (keeps the assembly
method "untouched" in spirit). Option (a) is the minimum change and is the most 
honest reading of the slice bodies. **Recommended: tighten L1 to option (a).**
