`TriggerIngressResponse` into the `triggerFireResponseSchema` shape 
(`{accepted:true, eventId, triggerId, status}`) — and explicitly does **not** 
call `verifier.verify` directly, so the real ingress path (which is what L9 is 
asserting) is exercised end-to-end.
